    <title><![CDATA[我的第一篇文章]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.aimonkey.cn/2015/12/29/My-First-Post/"/>
    <id>http://www.aimonkey.cn/2015/12/29/My-First-Post/</id>
    <published>2015-12-29T11:34:49.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-12-31T10:00:00.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到Brance的博客，这将是我使用Hexo记录的第一篇博客,这个<a href="https://hexo.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">Hexo</a>真的很强大，我将不遗余力使用它!</p>
<p><img src="http://7xpnu3.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/image%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84github.png" alt="brance github"></p>
<h2 id="Hexo_u7684_u7B80_u5355_u4F7F_u7528"><a href="#Hexo_u7684_u7B80_u5355_u4F7F_u7528" class="headerlink" title="Hexo的简单使用"></a>Hexo的简单使用</h2><h3 id="u521B_u5EFA_u65B0_u535A_u5BA2"><a href="#u521B_u5EFA_u65B0_u535A_u5BA2" class="headerlink" title="创建新博客"></a>创建新博客</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My First Post"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>More info:<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writinh.html" target="_blank" rel="external">Writing</a></p>
<h3 id="u5F00_u542F_u672C_u5730_u670D_u52A1"><a href="#u5F00_u542F_u672C_u5730_u670D_u52A1" class="headerlink" title="开启本地服务"></a>开启本地服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server  </span><br><span class="line">或 </span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>
<h3 id="u5E38_u7528_u547D_u4EE4_u96C6_u5408"><a href="#u5E38_u7528_u547D_u4EE4_u96C6_u5408" class="headerlink" title="常用命令集合"></a>常用命令集合</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"postName"</span>       <span class="comment">#新建文章</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new photo <span class="string">"photoPostName"</span> <span class="comment">#新建照片文章</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new page <span class="string">"pageName"</span>  <span class="comment">#新建页面</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo generate             <span class="comment">#生成静态页面至public目录</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo server               <span class="comment">#开启预览访问端口(默认端口4000,'ctrl + c' 关闭服务)</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo deploy               <span class="comment">#将.deploy目录部署到github上</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo <span class="built_in">help</span>                 <span class="comment">#查看帮助</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo version              <span class="comment">#查看Hexo版本</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="u590D_u5408_u547D_u4EE4"><a href="#u590D_u5408_u547D_u4EE4" class="headerlink" title="复合命令"></a>复合命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server -g <span class="comment">#生成并开启服务</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo deploy -g <span class="comment">#生成并部署到github</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="u5F15_u7528_u5757_u7684_u4F7F_u7528_uFF1A"><a href="#u5F15_u7528_u5757_u7684_u4F7F_u7528_uFF1A" class="headerlink" title="引用块的使用："></a>引用块的使用：</h3><blockquote><p>content</p>
<footer><strong>[author] [link] [source_link_title]</strong></footer></blockquote>
<h5 id="u63D2_u5165_u7F51_u7AD9_u56FE_u6807"><a href="#u63D2_u5165_u7F51_u7AD9_u56FE_u6807" class="headerlink" title="插入网站图标"></a>插入网站图标</h5><p>看一下hexo\themes\modernist\layout_partial\head.ejs</p>
<blockquote><p>&lt; link rel=”icon” type=”image/x-icon” href=”&lt;%- config.root %&gt;favicon.ico” &gt;</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
